## Installation

### Installing via Smithery

To install mcp-secops-soar for Claude Desktop automatically via
[Smithery](https://smithery.ai/server/@emeryray2002/mcp-secops-soar):

```bash
npx -y @smithery/cli install @emeryray2002/mcp-secops-soar --client claude
```

### Manual Installation

1.  Install the package:

```bash
pip install -e .
```

1.  Set up your environment variables:

```bash
export TBD
```

## Requirements

-   Python 3.11+
-   A Google Cloud account with Chronicle Security Operations enabled
-   Proper authentication configured

## Usage

### Running the MCP Server

```bash
python main.py
```

